user_description: Immunologist working on pregnancy at @ImperialCollege | equality and diversity in STEM | she/her | Because VikiLovesNKCells was too long for Twitter
text:
The @RCObsGyn and @MidwivesRCM recommends that you get your #CovidVaccine if you are #pregnant. 

Getting vaccinated is not associated with increased risk of any pregnancy complications but getting COVID puts you at increased risk of preterm birth.
